OL,3,CPair jailed after attempt to transport
OL,4,Cfamily into UK in van
OL,6,FTwo people smugglers who tried to
OL,7,Fsmuggle a family-of-five from
OL,8,FAfghanistan into the country hidden in
OL,9,Fa rubbish-filled van have been jailed.
OL,11,FThe youngest child was "extremely
OL,12,Funwell and drifting in and out of
OL,13,Fconsciousness" when the family were
OL,14,Fdiscovered by Border Force officers in
OL,15,FCoquelles, in France, on August 27
OL,16,F2018.
