OL,3,CPair jailed after attempt to transport
OL,4,Cfamily into UK in van
OL,6,FJosh Mallaburn, 33, and Liam Cronin,
OL,7,F34, were convicted of assisting
OL,8,Funlawful immigration transporting the
OL,9,Ffamily following a trial at Maidstone
OL,10,FCrown Court in October.
OL,12,FThe businessman and bricklayer from
OL,13,FHemel Hempstead, Hertfordshire, were
OL,14,Feach sentenced to three years and
OL,15,Fthree months' imprisonment on Friday,
OL,16,Fsix years after they committed the
OL,17,Foffences.
