OL,4,Cfamily into UK in van
OL,6,FSentencing them, Recorder Nicola
OL,7,FMakanjuola said their offences
OL,8,Fthreatened UK borders and that
OL,9,Fsentences for this crime were "heavy"
OL,10,Fand intended to deter others.
OL,12,FShe said she had no doubt the "one-off
OL,13,Fincident" was for commercial gain,
OL,14,Falthough there was no evidence how
OL,15,Fmuch the pair benefited financially.
