OL,6,FThe judge added that among the reasons
OL,7,Fshe had reduced the sentences from
OL,8,Ffour years in prison, was that the
OL,9,Fpair, who are both fathers, had had
OL,10,Fthe proceedings "hanging over their
OL,11,Fheads for six years".
OL,13,FThey will serve half of their sentence
OL,14,Fin custody and half on licence.
OL,16,FThe court also heard that the family
OL,17,Finvolved in the incident were able to
OL,18,Fenter the UK and were granted asylum
OL,19,Fin 2022.
