OL,4,Cfamily into UK in van
OL,6,FReacting to the sentencing, Home
OL,7,FOffice criminal and financial
OL,8,Finvestigations regional lead, Chris
OL,9,FFoster, said the move sent a strong
OL,10,Fmessage to others considering getting
OL,11,Finvolved in the trade.
OL,13,F"In the back of that van was a lot of
OL,14,Ffishing equipment and building
OL,15,Fequipment, they were held in pretty
OL,16,Fsqualid and dangerous conditions," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@bO]
