OL,6,F"There was a real threat those people
OL,7,Fcould have died in that van, if there
OL,8,Fhad been an accident, they could have
OL,9,Fbeen seriously injured.
OL,11,F"It's people like Mallaburn and Cronin
OL,12,Fpreying on families like this,
OL,13,Fdesperate people, and they are selling
OL,14,Fthem a dream, it's clearly done for
OL,15,Fmonetary purposes."
OL,17,FMr Foster also said work continued to
OL,18,Fidentify co-conspirators in the case
OL,19,Fand that he believed the Government's
OL,20,Fnew Border Security Command would make
OL,21,Ftheir approach "even more powerful".
