OL,6,FOn changes seen so far, he said: "It's
OL,7,Fearly days, the structure is still
OL,8,Fbeing built.
OL,10,F"But what I have seen, we were
OL,11,Falready, in my opinion, working very
OL,12,Fhard, it's more cohesive now I
OL,13,Fbelieve, I think we're going to see
OL,14,Fsome real successes with it."
OL,16,FThe case on Friday comes as another
OL,17,Ftwo people smugglers were jailed on
OL,18,FMonday for helping 14 Iranian
OL,19,Fnationals come to the UK by plane,
OL,20,Fusing forged Bulgarian passports, the
OL,21,FHome Office said.
