OL,6,FDaniel Belza, 49, of Purley, and Jalal
OL,7,FSaraei Adeh, 45, of London, were
OL,8,Fjailed for facilitating illegal entry
OL,9,Fbetween May and October 2022, after
OL,10,Fmaking more than #250,000 from the
OL,11,Foperation, the government department
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe pair were sentenced to a combined
OL,15,Feight years in prison at Croydon Crown
OL,16,FCourt.
